      right: ["Adrenal crisis: severe hypotension unresponsive to fluids alone","Altered mental status progressing to obtundation or coma","Severe hyponatremia with seizure risk","Hyperkalemia with cardiac dysrhythmias","Profound hypoglycemia"]
